{"tid":1749073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［區選］今日11.24日任！監察師","createTime":"2019-11-24T01:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T05:11:13.000Z","uid":36807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b04570f1ce24c2673095c815b991b9fd5c37540","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:47:08.000Z","msg":"-------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">說服屋企人投票</span></span></strong><br />\n24號當日一早約屋企人食個靚飯再一齊去投票<br />\n又或者做孝子賢孫<br />\n接出嚟老人院陪一日都好正常 或者投完票去個短程旅行<br />\n唔好俾你嘅家人成為保皇黨嘅工具<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留意自己屋企地址有冇俾人利用</span></span></strong><br />\n（雖然已經講到明就算有投訴都唔會影響到今屆投票權，但係呢啲嘢一定一定要主動去制止，以免影響以後）<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處，會於本月寄出「投票通知卡」。<br />\n請各選民務必留意有關來函，核對個人身份。如收到不明人士用了你的地址，請參閱選舉事務處職員的建議(見LINK)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24594/2019區議會選舉-選民資料-24594/選民資料\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F24594%2F2019%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-24594%2F%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=ed3c8577\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24594/2019區議會選舉-選民資料-24594/選民資料</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做個盡責公民 監察選舉</span></span></strong><br />\n你唔單止可以去監票 仲可以留意下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXO3QO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXO3QO1.jpg&h=d0f5d869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n監察<strong>1⃣票站內/禁止宣傳區</strong><br />\n會唔會有人展示咗選舉單張宣傳品（掌心雷etc）？因為該處係唔可以展示任何選舉宣傳品。<br />\n如有，可向當值票站主任投訴<br />\n<strong>記低當時選舉主任名丶職位 丶發生時間丶詳情。但需要留意任何人士如無選管會成員或票站主任准許，在票站內拍照、錄影或錄音，均屬違法，可被判罰款5,000元及監禁六個月，你可以用紙筆記低記錄。</strong><br />\n<br />\n監察<strong>2⃣留意屋苑/附近老人院會唔會有可疑人士</strong><br />\n有班人有一定票源 佢哋會派人係屋苑點名<br />\n方便佢哋計票 <br />\n你住緊嘅地方有可疑人士係附近徘徊 你感到不安可以向保安反映 投訴要求佢跟進（雖然有機會真係住喺度）監察佢跟進情況<br />\n處理投訴期間 呢班點票黨已經冇咁容易可以點到名 數人數亦都冇咁準確 <br />\n可以做嘅就係合法情況下打亂佢部署<br />\n<br />\n監察<strong>3⃣買票（現金或利益）</strong><br />\n假如真係有人向你屋企人買票<br />\n呢啲咁影響選舉公義嘅嘢 一定需要舉報<br />\n同埋告知你屋企人配合咁樣做係違法<br />\n有刑事責任 同時必須要保留一切記錄（錄音丶電話紀錄等等）<br />\n報ICAC<br />\n<br />\n監察<strong>4⃣勿幫保皇計人數</strong><br />\n通常票站門口會有xxx協會做問卷<br />\n任何調查都好 會影響票源！<br />\n佢哋係親共 幫保皇黨配票/或者睇下邊度需要催票 呢班人係針對佢哋掌握左嘅票源以外去做分析<br />\n你可以答佢投左民建聯/認真9UP就得 <br />\n分數唔好俾滿分 會太假 <br />\n佢冇權查你身分證 你唔一定係後生仔<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">配合亂做問卷呢個係超級重要 點解？</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>因為問卷結果會影響到保皇人手丶摏腳（即係大廈外點名既可疑人士）丶輪椅/資源要調動去邊<br />\n保皇黨計票係好準 因為佢會有摏腳每幢公屋樓下數票 + 上門推阿婆去投 + 一堆種票<br />\n合法地打亂佢哋點票計劃無風險<br />\n一定要答投咗佢！</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［做問卷記得要保障自己私人資料］</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n監察<strong>5⃣留意下有冇不合理活動</strong><br />\n例如突然間有一條輪椅隊 係團隊式咁樣運作 身上有奇怪識別物（唔同顏色嘅扣針絲帶髮夾等等）<br />\n又或者旅遊巴大隊拉人落嚟etc<br />\n你可以向信任嘅非保皇團隊反應呢啲異常<br />\n佢哋有權向票站主任投訴<br />\n投訴未必有用 但可以打亂佢哋計劃<br />\n亦都係合法合理嘅<br />\n<br />\n監察<strong>6⃣就住違規行為報料</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1693229/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1693229/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n「選舉觀察計劃」報料熱線 Election Observation Hotline<br />\nTelegram: @hotline19hkeop<br />\nWhatsApp: +85297424472<br />\n又或者報料俾傳媒記者（蘋果丶有線丶立場）<br />\n監察7️⃣<br />\n幫傳真社寫做記錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuhY9X0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuhY9X0.png&h=08147a20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuTagC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuTagC1.jpg&h=e5757ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>精明投票</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當日唔需要着黑衫表態 <br />\n唔好俾對家用呢樣嘢預測人數 </span><br />\n<strong>遇到任何野都要諗一諗：會唔會影響到選舉結果呢</strong><br />\n例如當日比選票你嘅時候 有塗污甚至損毁 請即時向票站人員反映更換 因為呢張將會係無效選票<br />\n檢查已換取嘅票 正式投票後亦可以進行投訴 或者報備比記者聽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89KdemB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89KdemB.jpg&h=1d7b938e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">票站外有任何異常記得影底！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ad9433ee513ec8a10ccab4cc60715f5470eb7d18","tid":1749073,"uid":84431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:51:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37fa7f9143afc18db5cd22a692fdcd7466815221","tid":1749073,"uid":84431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T01:52:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5f1c61949ab8f8a8a5069a63a28ebfea390f364","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得閒嘅夜晚可以去埋監票</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fab338a0c4cab620cf3f80d2cd76b70b623ae789","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJ2yeAa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJ2yeAa.png&h=eaa3cc2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f8064333ca0e2225b189160ef1252d8c5bd0f7f","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b26b513a3382b9aa5fe3dc6337f3c2013faaade","tid":1749073,"uid":113148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37bffbf9ba98600141cc6db0189be7def2b39bf0","tid":1749073,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506a408a61fe84a5bfa2632db445a61d23711a3d","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"Facebook今日有你投左票未嘅選項<br />\n大家記得千其唔好㩒！  你個人紀錄 你睇開咩page，留開咩言，facebook全部都記錄左，如果你㩒左已投，佢可以估到你地投左咩陣營咩人。準確率比票站民調一定高N倍，仲要係即時。"},{"pid":"c64d55a089221699964ac3198670a7ffc6a28e00","tid":1749073,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"有人話票站外有放低枝cam影住<br />\n如果見到問吓係咩人擺？"},{"pid":"5d921063e8778bd013322df70ae783a5e143df37","tid":1749073,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249a37d400a4618d620537dfd82f451c6c08480a","tid":1749073,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec2da4b685d54f84df883a4c7234a9100c5d348","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAfG77C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAfG77C.jpg&h=076783a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRcN3FY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRcN3FY.jpg&h=d8d5ffee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a1a815692a3546daf6b2617724fd40fccd2f225","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c64d55a089221699964ac3198670a7ffc6a28e00","tid":1749073,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"有人話票站外有放低枝cam影住<br />\n如果見到問吓係咩人擺？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"「突發」請留意票站外有冇人身上掛住個cam<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1749152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1749152</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"096