r />\n如果見到問吓係咩人擺？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"唔知，我都見到有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"拍片/相<br />\n報料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynB3Cfp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynB3Cfp.png&h=037bf742&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tu8Om4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tu8Om4.jpg&h=88111937&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53111a027993574c3f155daadab0a56434208ed0","tid":1749073,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T05:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JznirE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJznirE1.jpg&h=83bfd4b5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}